OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Richard
OL,4,CWillis
OL,6,FRichard Willis, Age 100, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 30 July 2024
OL,10,FDied October 2024
OL,12,FFirst lieutenant on a tank landing
OL,13,Fcraft, Mr Willis helped ferry US
OL,14,Ftroops and tanks to Utah Beach on D-
OL,15,FDay.
OL,17,FUtah was one of the two American
OL,18,Fbeaches and the first troops came
OL,19,Fashore at about 6.30am.
