OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Richard
OL,4,CWillis
OL,6,FLCT 898 was the target of machine gun
OL,7,Ffire when it arrived and there were
OL,8,Falready burnt and submerged tanks.
OL,10,FMr Willis said: "As far as I was
OL,11,Fconcerned we were far too big to go
OL,12,Fdown on one of the beaches.
OL,14,F"However, that didn't matter - we
OL,15,Fwent. I was very worried about getting
OL,16,Fthe tanks off because that was our
OL,17,Fmission.
OL,19,F"Once we had done that we could really
OL,20,Fgo home.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
