OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Richard
OL,4,CWillis
OL,6,F"We were trying to get enough space to
OL,7,Fget all the tanks off. The door was
OL,8,Fright at the end, at the bow. But I
OL,9,Fwas in the tank area and I remember a
OL,10,Fbig bang and then later a bang on the
OL,11,Fother side.
OL,13,F"We were hit on both sides and the
OL,14,Fdoor wouldn't move one way or the
OL,15,Fother.
