OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Richard
OL,4,CWillis
OL,6,FHe said: "He had the engine running
OL,7,Fand he was saying he wanted to go
OL,8,Fbecause it was so urgent to go. I said
OL,9,Fthis is nonsense but unfortunately I
OL,10,Fwaved and I think he thought I was
OL,11,Fwaving him off. And the jeep sank.
OL,13,F"I saw his hat, the American's hat
OL,14,Ffloat down in the water."
OL,16,FMr Willis was hit in the leg by
OL,17,Fshrapnel whilst on board and did not
OL,18,Fnotice at first that he was wounded.
OL,19,FHe was taken off the vessel in a
OL,20,Fstretcher.
